description: The image features the Amazon logo, which consists of the word "amazon" in white text with a curved yellow arrow running from "a" to "z" on a dark background.
The image shows a shiny, red apple with a small stem on top, sitting against a white background.
The image features the colorful logo of Google, with a magnifying glass incorporated into the letter "o."
The image displays the logo of Meta, featuring a stylized blue infinity symbol next to the name "Meta" in dark text.
The image features the iconic black Nike logo, which consists of the word "NIKE" in bold lettering alongside the recognizable swoosh symbol.
The image shows a vibrant orange fruit with a glossy skin and a green leaf attached to its stem.
The image shows a whole pineapple with a rough, spiky exterior and a crown of green leaves on top.
